msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.52:0.2"
msgid "6. Nīvaraṇavagga "
msgstr "6. Hindrances "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.52:0.3"
msgid "52. Akusalarāsisutta "
msgstr "52. A Heap of the Unskillful "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.65, sc1
#. VAR: vadamāno pañca nīvaraṇe → ime pañcanīvaraṇe (bj)
msgctxt "an5.52:1.1"
msgid "“Akusalarāsīti, bhikkhave, vadamāno pañca nīvaraṇe sammā vadamāno vadeyya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, rightly speaking, you’d call the five hindrances a ‘heap of the unskillful’. "

#. VAR: hāyaṃ → hayaṃ (bj, pts1) | cāyaṃ (s1-3, km) | sāyaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an5.52:1.2"
msgid "Kevalo hāyaṃ, bhikkhave, akusalarāsi yadidaṃ pañca nīvaraṇā. "
msgstr "For these five hindrances are entirely a heap of the unskillful. "

msgctxt "an5.52:1.3"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.52:1.4"
msgid "Kāmacchandanīvaraṇaṃ, byāpādanīvaraṇaṃ, thinamiddhanīvaraṇaṃ, uddhaccakukkuccanīvaraṇaṃ, vicikicchānīvaraṇaṃ. "
msgstr "The hindrances of sensual desire, ill will, dullness and drowsiness, restlessness and remorse, and doubt. "

msgctxt "an5.52:1.5"
msgid "Akusalarāsīti, bhikkhave, vadamāno ime pañca nīvaraṇe sammā vadamāno vadeyya. "
msgstr "Rightly speaking, you’d call these five hindrances a ‘heap of the unskillful’. "

msgctxt "an5.52:1.6"
msgid "Kevalo hāyaṃ, bhikkhave, akusalarāsi yadidaṃ pañca nīvaraṇā”ti. "
msgstr "For these five hindrances are entirely a heap of the unskillful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.52:1.7"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

